description:
Come holiday shopping with us! In this bonus episode, Jenn and Jess share the beauty gifts they're giving friends, family—and each other! All the goodies are from Ulta Beauty—with a special focus on brands from SPARKED at Ulta Beauty™—so if you're inspired to do some of your own gift giving, you know exactly where to find everything. This commercial-free podcast is produced in partnership with Ulta Beauty. They are dedicated to bringing up-and-coming brands to beauty lovers. Visit ulta.com/sparked to find out more and shop the SPARKED virtual experience. 


Want more Fat Mascara?
